sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator
    participant Odoo as Odoo control plane
    participant API as Deployment API
    participant DB as API PostgreSQL
    participant Host as Deployment Host
    participant Docker as Docker Compose
    participant Nginx as nginx

    Operator->>Odoo: Click Create/Redeploy
    Odoo->>Odoo: Build YAML manifest
    Odoo->>API: PUT /api/instances/{name}/manifest
    API->>API: Validate manifest and compute SHA
    API->>DB: Store instance, history, task
    API-->>Odoo: 202 Accepted task_id
    API->>Host: SSH connect
    Host->>Host: Create /srv/doodba/{instance}/{sha}
    API->>Host: Upload rendered workspace
    Host->>Host: Run gitaggregate
    Host->>Docker: docker compose up -d --wait
    Host->>Docker: bootstrap or upgrade Odoo
    Host->>Nginx: Write vhost, nginx -t, reload
    API->>DB: Mark task success/failure and logs
    Odoo->>API: Poll /api/tasks/bulk
    Odoo->>API: Fetch logs/status
    Odoo->>Odoo: Mirror remote state
